        <mxCell id="notes-title" value="&lt;b&gt;NOTES&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="45" y="695" width="60" height="18" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="notes-text" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;1. PoE injector on Witty Pi switched 12V rail &amp;mdash;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;camera power-cycles in sync with Pi.&lt;br&gt;2. No heaters (Sukabumi tropical climate,&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;solar power budget constraint).&lt;br&gt;3. Conformal coating MG 422C on all PCBs.&lt;br&gt;4. Dielectric grease on outdoor connections.&lt;br&gt;5. Gore vent for pressure equalization.&lt;br&gt;6. Carrier: Telkomsel (Indonesia).&lt;br&gt;7. Peak draw: ~42W (3.5A @ 12V).&lt;br&gt;8. Cycle: 2.5 min ON / 12.5 min SLEEP&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(96 cycles/day).&lt;br&gt;9. ANNKE C1200 built-in IR &amp;mdash;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;no separate illuminator needed.&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="715" width="290" height="185" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

